#PAGINA LAYER
#String text
Display amount of cave dust fallen on tile when mining if you were present when it happened.\n\nHolding $b{$col[255,128,0]{SHIFT}} while activating this will turn on minesweeper cursor:\n• $col[255,128,0]{Clicking} will add 'danger' [$font[monospaced,10]{$col[240,32,100]{$b{×}}}] marker on the tile.\n• $col[255,128,0]{ALT+Click} will add 'safe' [$font[monospaced,10]{$col[32,220,80]{$b{·}}}] marker to the tile.\n• $col[255,128,0]{SHIFT+Click} will add 'maybe' [$font[monospaced,10]{$col[193,87,251]{$b{?}}}] to the tile.\n• $col[255,128,0]{CTRL+Click} will remove marker from the tile.\n\nThese markers can be placed on tiles with numbers, if needed.
